headline: Truist announces first-quarter 2025 earnings call details
summary: Truist Financial Corporation (NYSE: TFC) will report first-quarter 2025 financial results before the market opens on Thursday, April 17, 2025. Chairman and Chief Executive Officer Bill Rogers and Chief Financial Officer Mike Maguire will host a conference call to review the company's financial results at 8 a.m. ET.
